headline: General Dynamics Electric Boat awarded $1 billion contract modification for long lead time material for Virginia-class submarines
summary: General Dynamics Electric Boat, a business unit of General Dynamics (NYSE: GD), announced today it has been awarded a $1 billion undefinitized contract modification allowing Electric Boat to purchase long lead time materials for Virginia Class Block VI submarines as detailed in the U.S. Department of Defense contract announcement.
